# Installing PiAware on an Existing dump1090 Instance

## Overview

If you are running an ADS-B receiver with dump1090 on a Raspberry Pi, you can install the PiAware package to transmit your ADS-B receiver data to FlightAware. This guide will walk you through the steps to installp PiAware on your existing dump1090 instance.

## Requirements

- Raspberry Pi with Raspberry Pi OS (Bookworm, Bullseye, or Buster)
- Internet connection
- Access to a command line shell on the Pi
- SSH access enabled on the Raspberry Pi

## Steps

### 1. Install the Latest OS Updates and Reboot

